## Select Control
A select control is a UI element that allows users to choose one option from a dropdown list.

It typically consists of a rectangular box displaying the selected option and an arrow indicating expandable options.
Users can click or tap to reveal the list and select a different option.
It's widely used for forms and settings where predefined choices are required.
